<lb ed="GA" n="0156a07"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0156a08"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0156a09"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="5"><cb:jhead>鄧尉聖恩寺志卷之五<note place="inline">終</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>